<bibRefCitation id="8054AAC96A7D4BDF4A94F730B8F809E0" author="Monros, F" journalOrPublisher="Acta Zoologica Lilloana" pageId="61" pageNumber="72" pagination="489 - 672" title="Revision de las especies argentinas de Chlamisinae (Col., Chrysomelidae) (5 ª contribucion al conocimiento de Chlamisinae)." volume="10" year="1951 c">
<normalizedToken id="97A959AA89E9FBAB08BF64CFCF760320" originalValue="Monrós">Monros</normalizedToken>
1951c
</bibRefCitation>
). Six of the 21 Neotropical species are present in Argentina.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
